faq.Question: What is the difference between a web designer and a web developer?
faq.Answer: Web designers are responsible for the look and feel of a website. Web developers are responsible for the functionality of a website.

faq.Question: What is the difference between a front-end developer and a back-end developer?
faq.Answer: Front-end developers are responsible for the look and feel of a website. Back-end developers are responsible for the functionality of a website.
